6d044215d280e72331","tid":1522022,"uid":58555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:58:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed51064da60b3ad751f9dfe511dadd422a837038","tid":1522022,"uid":259901,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:58:34.000Z","msg":"其實你著過上面就會有死皮留低<br />\n入墳場化寶爐燒左佢啦"},{"pid":"434219aed8fa82e57bdf8fdb2330f660a25cdc49","tid":1522022,"uid":58555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:59:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c410a7a07cddb66b1e5a2958296c44c6f0db547","tid":1522022,"uid":115977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:59:59.000Z","msg":"呼籲各區街坊，帶齊以下物品<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 長袖衫+褲<br />\n2. 鞋+襪<br />\n3. 帽<br />\n4. 袋<br />\n5. 酒精濕紙巾/落妝水<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">往各區地鐵及巴士站接仔女放學</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>請盡一分力，守護同路人，守護香港未來</strong></span>"},{"pid":"5271e45f6038819b1fc8fcfe4cd07e974aa1daed","tid":1522022,"uid":139282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:02:04.000Z","msg":"求吓大家幫手copy呢段去spread開啊<br />\n<br />\n［化學］如何清洗顏色水劑（含acrylics/PMMA）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1406604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1406604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. hot sodium carbonate solution</span><br />\n<br />\n-蘇打水，溫度50度或更高，建議自己開，落多小小都唔怕<br />\n（同小蘇打sodium bicarbonate有啲分別，唔知bicarbonate效果係點）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.消毒火酒（酒精）/含消毒火酒成份濕紙巾</span><br />\n<br />\n3<span style=\"color: red;\">.化妝水</span>/卸妝水/洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n可以洗到有acrylics/PMMA嘅顏料<br />\n<br />\n紅字係考慮完availability, effectiveness, usefulness, side-effects嘅建議<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另外衫褲鞋襪可以先噴防水噴霧<br />\n中招就唔好留直接dum咗佢</span><br />\n<br />\n消毒火酒：<br />\n易買 平 可用作消毒 但係多用傷皮膚<br />\n化/卸妝水：<br />\n女仔會有 比較唔傷皮膚 但貴 同埋唔同牌子效果可能會有差異<br />\n<br />\n其他建議：<br />\n#67 威猛先生玻璃劑<br />\n#91 含酒精成分濕紙巾<br />\n#117 大塊顏料可以待乾再成塊搣<br />\n<br />\n#127<br />\n可以搽定凡士林/hand cream<br />\n保持皮膚濕潤方便移除顏料<br />\n<br />\n#145<br />\n唔敢去五金可以去模型舖買Mr Color paint remover/Mr Color tool cleaner，冇就買住水性油天拿水頂住先<br />\n<br />\n#148<br />\n補充使用順序：<br />\n先用水性油天拿水或者75%酒精捽<br />\n好頑固捽唔到嗰啲先用paint remover/tool cleaner<br />\n因為用完呢兩隻，啲顏料會變硝基，用唔返酒精<br />\n最後都唔得先好用洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n#164<br />\n凡士林coating，logon $50 gel removal<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">#216<br />\n應該冇加料 UV燈照過安全，番簡水、梳打水可行</span><br />\n<br />\n#252<br />\n綠藻濃縮液+薑，開水沖，唔傷皮膚"},{"pid":"bf6a0b304da5f32759088d528ccbc44c884600f7","tid":1522022,"uid":58555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:02:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e49d906227dd2747fd4dd0bfd48d8c10af0c5f0","tid":1522022,"uid":81084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:02:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"38501ffd548a04a255e7e196148e6ef4d814ea71","tid":1522022,"uid":58555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:05:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd903110c2f6f39484496bbe18e0f3e084d8a841","tid":1522022,"uid":58555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:07:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9afa548095fc46d0f5557a4cb761d0eb7046d9d","tid":1522022,"uid":115977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:11:28.000Z","msg":"呼籲各區街坊，帶齊以下物品<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 長袖衫+褲<br />\n2. 鞋+襪<br />\n3. 帽<br />\n4. 袋<br />\n5. 酒精濕紙巾/落妝水<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">往各區地鐵及巴士站接仔女放學</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>請盡一分力，守護同路人，守護香港未來</strong></span>"},{"pid":"f511135c0d409c01cb8e380dda9682bb55536419","tid":1522022,"uid":58555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:11:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}